**Query #4**

    -- 2. Subquery in WHERE (Correlated)
    -- Employees earning ABOVE their department average
    SELECT e1.name, e1.department, e1.salary
    FROM Employees e1
    WHERE e1.salary > (
        SELECT AVG(e2.salary)
        FROM Employees e2
        WHERE e2.department = e1.department
    );

| name  | department | salary |
| ----- | ---------- | ------ |
| Bob   | HR         | 50000  |
| David | IT         | 70000  |

